The paper deals with generating and comprehending descriptions of objects in images, which is a task that involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method proposed in the paper is based on deep learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the creation of a new dataset, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves organizing and retrieving data.
